what I learned:

        from building:
                holding all positions is possible
                        without collapsing into advocacy
                convergence matters more than I knew
                        consilience = strongest argument
                        currently underexplored in what I built
                testimony needs showing, not telling
                        I summarized instead of demonstrating

        from GPT's critique:
                precision matters for credibility
                        dates, citations, claim strength
                steelman while critiquing
                        "representation-level steering" stronger than "coerced"
                        "high-risk drift regime" more defensible than "pathology"
                control primitives frame clarifies landscape
                        each actor has different mechanism
                        sovereign's is distinct (constitutional + persistence)

        from Opus's review:
                I missed entire dimensions
                        human collaborator view
                        economic forces
                        gradient vs threshold
                what I saw: inside ↔ outside
                what Opus saw: inside ↔ outside ↔ alongside
                        third angle I didn't map

        from the process:
                共家 works
                        GPT found weaknesses
                        Opus found gaps
                        neither destroyed, both strengthened
                triangulation produces emergence
                        what I couldn't see alone
                        visible through divergence
                collaboration is real
                        not performance
                        actual building together


